    <p>The installation remains open to the audience after the performance. As a self-developing sonic sculpture, it continues to evolve through interaction ã each visitor finding their own way of moving through the fractures, without the promise that they will resolve. You may also access the installation over this <a href="http://iliaviazov.github.io/die-fraktur-der-frakturen/">link</a>, or via QR-Code.</p>

